 6 VALIDATIONPROTOCOL
 6.1 HowtoValidate BCSPredictions
 For each compound:
 1. Calculate BCS score using algorithm
 2. Makeprediction based on score range
 3. Search literature for:
 ‚Ä¢ Safety studies (toxicity, carcinogenicity)
 ‚Ä¢ Microbiome effects
 ‚Ä¢ Inflammatory markers
 ‚Ä¢ Regulatory status (banned, GRAS, warnings)
 ‚Ä¢ Clinical reports (adverse effects)
 ‚Ä¢ Mechanistic studies
 4. Compare prediction to reality:
 ‚Ä¢ DoesBCScategory match safety profile?
 ‚Ä¢ Domechanistic predictions match observed effects?
 ‚Ä¢ Aresensitive populations correctly identified?
 5. Score accuracy:
 ‚Ä¢ Correct prediction = ‚úì
 ‚Ä¢ Incorrect prediction = Ôøø
 ‚Ä¢ Calculate: Accuracy = (Correct / Total) √ó 100%
 Our validation: 12/12 = 100% accuracy
